1
00:00:00,273 --> 00:00:00,873
Father...

2
00:00:02,060 --> 00:00:03,320
Well met, my son.

3
00:00:03,769 --> 00:00:05,260
It's been a long time.

4
00:00:06,149 --> 00:00:08,300
I was hoping we would not see each other
again.

5
00:00:08,850 --> 00:00:10,780
I can't allow you to leave here,
Father.

6
00:00:11,610 --> 00:00:14,060
You have ever been the ally of humans?

7
00:00:14,700 --> 00:00:17,240
Have you forgotten what they did to your
mother?

8
00:00:18,270 --> 00:00:20,420
Think you I would forget such a thing?

9
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:24,100
No, but neither do I seek revenge against
them.

10
00:00:24,900 --> 00:00:27,580
Still uttering the same nonsense.

11
00:00:28,080 --> 00:00:29,080
No matter.

12
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:33,618
Now is the time to put
aside your weak human

13
00:00:33,630 --> 00:00:37,440
side and join me in
remaking this world!

